{"id": "test-00040", "text": "Syria had taken the lead from their first serious attack in the seventh minute.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 5, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Syria"}]}
{"id": "test-00041", "text": "Nader Jokhadar headed a cross from the right by Ammar Awad into the top right corner of Kenichi Shimokawa's goal.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 14, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Nader Jokhadar"}, {"start": 48, "end": 58, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Ammar Awad"}, {"start": 88, "end": 105, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Kenichi Shimokawa"}]}
{"id": "test-00042", "text": "Japan then laid siege to the Syrian penalty area and had a goal disallowed for offside in the 16th minute.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 5, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Japan"}, {"start": 29, "end": 35, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Syrian"}]}
{"id": "test-00043", "text": "A minute later, Bitar produced a good double save, first from Kazuyoshi Miura's header and then blocked a Takagi follow-up shot.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 16, "end": 21, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bitar"}, {"start": 62, "end": 77, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Kazuyoshi Miura"}, {"start": 106, "end": 112, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Takagi"}]}
{"id": "test-00044", "text": "Bitar saved well again from Miura in the 37th minute, parrying away his header from a corner.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 5, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bitar"}, {"start": 28, "end": 33, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Miura"}]}
{"id": "test-00045", "text": "Japan started the second half brightly but Bitar denied them an equaliser when he dived to his right to save Naoki Soma's low drive in the 53rd minute.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 5, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Japan"}, {"start": 43, "end": 48, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bitar"}, {"start": 109, "end": 119, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Naoki Soma"}]}
{"id": "test-00046", "text": "Japan: 19 - Kenichi Shimokawa, 2 - Hiroshige Yanagimoto, 3 - Naoki Soma, 4 - Masami Ihara, 5 - Norio Omura, 6 - Motohiro Yamaguchi, 8 - Masakiyo Maezono (7 - Yasuto Honda 71), 9 - Takuya Takagi, 10 - Hiroshi Nanami, 11 - Kazuyoshi Miura, 15 - Hiroaki Morishima (14 - Masayuki Okano 75).", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 5, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Japan"}, {"start": 12, "end": 29, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Kenichi Shimokawa"}, {"start": 35, "end": 55, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Hiroshige Yanagimoto"}, {"start": 61, "end": 71, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Naoki Soma"}, {"start": 77, "end": 89, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Masami Ihara"}, {"start": 95, "end": 106, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Norio Omura"}, {"start": 112, "end": 130, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Motohiro Yamaguchi"}, {"start": 136, "end": 152, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Masakiyo Maezono"}, {"start": 158, "end": 170, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Yasuto Honda"}, {"start": 180, "end": 193, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Takuya Takagi"}, {"start": 200, "end": 214, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Hiroshi Nanami"}, {"start": 221, "end": 236, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Kazuyoshi Miura"}, {"start": 243, "end": 260, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Hiroaki Morishima"}, {"start": 267, "end": 281, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Masayuki Okano"}]}
{"id": "test-00047", "text": "Syria: 24 - Salem Bitar, 3 - Bachar Srour; 4 - Hassan Abbas, 5 - Tarek Jabban, 6 - Ammar Awad (9 - Louay Taleb 69), 8 - Nihad al-Boushi, 10 - Mohammed Afash, 12 - Ali Dib, 13 - Abdul Latif Helou (17 - Ammar Rihawiy 46), 14 - Khaled Zaher; 16 - Nader Jokhadar.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 5, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Syria"}, {"start": 12, "end": 23, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Salem Bitar"}, {"start": 29, "end": 41, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bachar Srour"}, {"start": 47, "end": 59, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Hassan Abbas"}, {"start": 65, "end": 77, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Tarek Jabban"}, {"start": 83, "end": 93, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Ammar Awad"}, {"start": 99, "end": 110, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Louay Taleb"}, {"start": 120, "end": 135, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Nihad al-Boushi"}, {"start": 142, "end": 156, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Mohammed Afash"}, {"start": 163, "end": 170, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Ali Dib"}, {"start": 177, "end": 194, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Abdul Latif Helou"}, {"start": 201, "end": 214, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Ammar Rihawiy"}, {"start": 225, "end": 237, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Khaled Zaher"}, {"start": 244, "end": 258, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Nader Jokhadar"}]}
